power.views.backend(request)[source]

Handles the calculation depending on the selected options by the user.

Parameters:

  • profile_in (str) – type of user power consumption profile

  • demand_in (int) – amount of power used in MW per month

  • saving (int) – savings in rand for the user

Returns:

all submitted details as well as savings

Return type:

str
